### Disclaimer

This software is provided for research and educational purposes. While we have 
made every effort to ensure accuracy and reliability, users should validate 
results independently for any critical applications.

The physics models and synthetic data generation are based on current 
understanding of stellar and planetary systems. As our knowledge evolves, 
the models may need updates to reflect new discoveries and improved theories.

